document_data.name: Cobh
document_data.mainbody: '''Cobh''' was a small town located in the kingdom of [[Callidyrr]] on the island of [[Alaron]] within the [[Moonshae Isles]].{{Cite interactive atlas}}{{Cite dungeon/196/Backdrop: The Moonshae Isles}}
document_data.Geography: Cobh was found in the county of [[Talffolk]] on Callidyrr's eastern coast on the [[Sea of Swords]]. The village was located north of [[Torriage Wood]] and south of [[Whitefish Bay]].
